  "comments": "This piece was on the South side of Chestnut, from 7 to 17th.  It was deconstructed some time before November, 2019 and most of the panels (but not the other elements) were restored and reinstalled on new shelters. The remaining pictures are of the missing panels. Some pictures have been edited to make vandalism on the metal illegible. ",
